# Email & Notifications

- Use Resend/SendGrid templates; bilingual subjects via locale param (`es-MX`, `en`).
- Trigger: order confirmed, OXXO voucher, shipment (Estafeta tracking), password reset, CRM assignment.

```typescript
await sendEmail({
  to: order.customer.email,
  template: 'order-confirmed',
  locale: order.locale,
  data: { orderNumber: order.id, totalMxn: formatMxn(order.total) },
});
```

- Include unsubscribe only for marketing; transactional emails need no marketing opt-out.
- No PII in logs; retry with exponential backoff; dead-letter failed sends for ops review.
- Test with sandbox inboxes before production; preview templates in both locales.
